      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="07f4516d2a9c851c" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>A berserker is a fierce warrior who can fly into a rage, greatly increasing their strength and hardiness. Many of them choose an animal such as a bear, wolf, or boar as their spiritual kin, wearing the skin of that animal and fighting like wild beasts.</source>
