      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="4713eac59065457a" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>Combat: Berserkers prefer large, heavy weapons such as axes, hammers, and greatswords, but they may use bows if they can’t easily get close to their foes.</source>
