      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="8835d05573390f9a" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>Interaction: Berserkers are the elites of some warrior cultures and enjoy physical competitions such as wrestling, throwing heavy items, and feasting. They dislike weak and cowardly folk, and do not tolerate insults to their strength or honor.</source>
